body_html:
@oscarriddle Hi. I just wonder how did your tensorflow serving load frozen model ? It seems that TensorRT could only optimize frozen model to frozen model. Did you recompile your serving to support tensorRT or do something to transfer frozen model to saved model?
Thanks.
